messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Please send medical. What is it, a medical emergency or something else?
There's a bad fight next door. One person is on the ground, and the other just got up.
What address?
Our address is 5304 Milegall Road. It's happening next door.
I think their last name is Cross or something similar.
Is it directly across the street or next door to you?
Right next door. There's a red truck outside.
Please hurry, I think he just ran someone over with the red truck.
He ran over somebody?
Yes, he's running them over in the driveway. Please hurry!
Ma'am, listen to me. I need to get some more information. Is it right next door?
Yes, right next door. He's running them over!
Please stay calm. So the person is in a red truck, running someone over repeatedly?
Yes, right next door.
If I'm looking at your house, is it on the right or the left?
It's on the right if you're looking at my house.
And it's a red truck doing this?
Yes. Please hurry!
They are already en route. What's your name, ma'am?
My husband's going out with a gun. Please hurry!
They are already en route. What's your phone number?
280-7314. Bill, get over here! Hurry!
Ma'am, they're already en route and moving as fast as they can. I need to ask some more questions.
Is the person who was run over getting up?
No, they are not getting up.
Is your husband back inside with the gun?
Yes, he's back inside.
Wait, it might have been a dog he ran over. We're not sure.
Ma'am, they are already en route. I need to be sure. So it might be a dog?
We're not sure, but it might be a dog. The truck is still there.
So the suspect vehicle is a red Jeep?
Yes, it looks like a red jeep.
Do you know the people over there?
We do, but not very well. The suspect's first name might be Josh.
Do you see any weapons?
No, but someone said he might have one. He's acting completely insane.
About two or three years ago, his dad shot himself over there.
Alright. My officers are en route. Is there anything else happening now?
No, but if he comes over here, I will shoot him.
Let's not discuss that. Just tell me what's happening in the yard.
I can't see anyone getting hit now. Maybe he went back inside.
So Josh went back into the house?
Yes, I think so.
Do you have Josh's last name?
No, I don't.
Alright, if anything else happens, call us back on 911.
Okay, thank you.
Bye.
